{"id":2257,"title":"[Correction of early liver dysfunction in patients with acute small bowel obstruction].","abstract":"Conducted a comprehensive examination and surgical treatment for acute obstruction of the small intestine (SI). It is established that, both before and after surgery to restore patency of SI is a significant violation of the functional state of the liver. This became the basis for the appointment of antioxidant therapy in the complex standard treatment. Using the solution reamberin promotes effective correction protein syntesis function disorders of the liver, reduces the severity of inflammation and stagnation in the hepatocytes, the severity of endogenous intoxication and the incidence of postoperative complications.","date":"2014-11-24","categories":"Digestive System Diseases","split":"test","url":"http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/25417278","annotations":[{"name":"Antioxidant","weight":0.869327,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Antioxidant"},{"name":"Protein","weight":0.829773,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Protein"},{"name":"Small intestine","weight":0.812688,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Small_intestine"},{"name":"Hepatocyte","weight":0.773888,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hepatocyte"},{"name":"Liver","weight":0.746246,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Liver"},{"name":"Inflammation","weight":0.745929,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Inflammation"},{"name":"Intestine","weight":0.743484,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Intestine"},{"name":"Incidence (epidemiology)","weight":0.71741,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Incidence_(epidemiology)"},{"name":"Bowel obstruction","weight":0.703039,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bowel_obstruction"},{"name":"Surgery","weight":0.689906,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Surgery"},{"name":"Complication (medicine)","weight":0.682664,"wi